---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <BaseHead title={`About Me | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Learn more about me and connect via social media." />
        <script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-1996789261448613" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
        <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32x32.png">
        <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon-16x16.png">
        <link rel="manifest" href="/site.webmanifest">
        <style>
            main {
                width: calc(100% - 2em);
                max-width: 720px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                padding: 2em 1em;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .hero-image {
                margin-bottom: 1em;
            }
            .hero-image img {
                max-width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                border-radius: 12px;
                box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            }
            h1 {
                margin: 0 0 1em 0;
                line-height: 1.2;
            }
            p {
                color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
                line-height: 1.6;
                margin-bottom: 2em;
            }
            .social-links {
                margin-top: 2em;
            }
            .social-links a {
                display: inline-block;
                margin: 0 1em;
                color: #007acc;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-weight: bold;
            }
            .social-links a:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <Header />
        <main>
            <div class="hero-image">
                <img src="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg" alt="About Me" width="720" height="360" />
            </div>
            <h1>关于 峙行</h1>
            <p>
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut
                labore et dolore magna aliqua. Vitae ultricies leo integer malesuada nunc vel risus commodo
                viverra. Adipiscing enim eu turpis egestas pretium. Euismod elementum nisi quis eleifend quam
                adipiscing.
            </p>
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="https://instagram.com/zhao1zhi" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
                <a href="https://x.com/zhao1zhi" target="_blank">X</a>
                <a href="https://youtube.com/@zhao1zhi" target="_blank">YouTube</a>
                <a href="weixin://youtube.com/@zhao1zhi" target="_blank">WeChat</a>
            </div>
        </main>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>
